k scheduling, and agricultural production, this book sets a new standard for measuring and interpreting child productivity in a subsistence farming community.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAgriculture durablexMexiquexYucatán (État). 0aEnfants mayasxConditions socialesxMexiquexYucatán (État). 0aEnfants mayasxConditions économiquesxMexiquexYucatán (État). 0aMaya childrenxEconomic conditionsxMexicoxYucatán (State). 0aMaya childrenxSocial conditionsxMexicoxYucatán (State). 0aMaya childrenzMexicozYucatán (State)xEconomic conditions. 0aMaya childrenzMexicozYucatán (State)xSocial conditions. 0aMayasxAgriculturexMexicoxYucatán (State). 0aMayasxAgriculturexMexiquexYucatán (État). 0aMayasxAgriculturezMexicozYucatán (State). 0aMayasxKinshipxMexicoxYucatán (State). 0aMayasxKinshipzMexicozYucatán (State). 0aMayasxParentéxMexiquexYucatán (État). 0aSustainable agriculturexMexicoxYucatán (State). 0aSustainable agriculturezMexicozYucatán (State). 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh1 aBoone, James L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLancaster, Jane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999z978311044221240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674039742423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780674039742/original  a978-3-11-044221-2  HUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999c1893d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK